SQL Question

Employee table: emp_id, emp_name, salary, department

Write SQL query to fetch:

employee name
salary
department
employees whose salary is greater than average salary of their department

Expected concepts:

AVG()
GROUP BY
subquery / join
-------------------------------------------------------------
select e.emp_name, e.salary, e.department from employee e
where salary > (select avg(e2.salary) from employee e2 where e.department = e2.department)